[[!meta title="Numerous security holes in Tails 1.3.2"]]

[[!tag security/fixed]]

Several security holes that affect Tails 1.3.2 are now fixed in
Tails 1.4

We **strongly** encourage you to [[upgrade to
Tails 1.4|news/version_1.4]] as soon as possible.

